description: Sehrt Seafood's menu offers a blend of Louisiana and southern style cuisines with an emphasis on fresh Gulf seafood. But no worries, we have dishes for land lovers too! Owner and Chef James Sehrt hand selects our seafood weekly in Louisiana to ensure we serve the highest quality food. Along with set menu items, seasonal specials will be highlighted. Let us share our love of food with you!
name: Sehrt Seafood Company
